{"tid":1891001,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"白領工會聽晚有「和你Live 」將有重要嘢要大家幫手！請大家支持下手足！","createTime":"2020-02-21T13:30:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T21:27:43.000Z","uid":152840,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"2d83a7e122b095428c8513f3a9c88a991f3a5a5b","tid":1891001,"uid":152840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T13:30:00.000Z","msg":"[香港白領工會和你Live]<br />\n自工會成立以來，本會都希望以live形式與各位會員互動。在不受時間同地點的限制下，令大家更了解本會目前的行動，並希望藉此聆聽各位會員對本會目前方向的意見。<br />\n<br />\n因此，本會將在2月22日(星期六)9pm 至 10pm，以Facebook Live 向各位會員以及正考慮入會中的白領簡述本會近期工作以及為聲援HAEA而發動的抗疫工業行動之成效。另外，我們成功邀請到響應罷工的會員作分享。<br />\n<br />\n最後，我們亦有即時問答環節，令大家可以與理事隔空交流！<br />\n=========================<br />\n白領同行，對抗疫症"},{"pid":"26c29aa09d841ecffe40affe4451edd0f7f1745b","tid":1891001,"uid":345458,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T13:30:09.000Z","msg":"多謝白領手足😭佢哋公會只係成立咗幾個月...但係無論係社運定係抗疫都為香港人付出咗好多..."},{"pid":"7e731e75441f08300ed40be09e4db56dfaae1752","tid":1891001,"uid":345458,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T13:30:29.000Z","msg":"佢哋聽日有嘢要咁多位手足幫手呀！<br />\n記得準時去睇佢哋Live撐場！佢哋仲有個「即問即答」環節...大家到時可以瘋狂問佢哋野"},{"pid":"b8f3863a0dfdda91da376f82cfb89b3c0d2516fd","tid":1891001,"uid":152840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T13:30:40.000Z","msg":"更多白領工會的最新消息：<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"http://facebook.com/hkwccu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fhkwccu&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAK3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=c37edff4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">facebook.com/hkwccu</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"http://instagram.com/hkwccu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhkwccu&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAK3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=941d086c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/hkwccu</a><br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"http://twitter.com/hkwccu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhkwccu&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7